data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. This property has been lovely cared for by the original owner. As a buyer you will be purchasing a home with a brand new roof, (to be installed prior to closing)  and there are money saving solar panels!  Significant savings on your HO insurance and monthly electric bills.    Exceptional floor plan with large rooms, vaulted ceilings, french doors, light and bright with an open concept  Kitchen overlooks, eating space, family room with a view of the backyard via french doors.  Step from the french doors onto the large lanai with private back yard and a view of trees and woods. This is a wonderful space to entertain, read a book or gather to watch sports.  The master bedroom overlooks the rear patio area as well with french door access. The master suite has a bonus room perfect for an office, nursery, gym or hobby room.  Master features an ample walk in closet, and large master bath with double sinks.  This split plan features 2 generous bedrooms, with a common bathroom all conveniently located near the utility room.   All  kitchen appliances stay, including washer and dryer and window treatments.   This home will not last, as rarely is a  home offered in this sought after neighborhood, conveniently located near schools, restaurants and shopping.  Veterans note, the home currently has a VA mortgage with low interest rate, assumable with qualifying.
